        "Str 3, Dex 16, Con 9, Int 2, Wis 12, Cha 5",
        "Base Atk +0; CMB +1; CMD 7",
        "Feats Run",
        "Skills Acrobatics +3 (Jumping +11), Stealth +13; Racial Modifiers +8 Jumping;"
      ],
      "SPECIAL ABILITIES": [
        "Carrot (Su) Once every 1d4 turns and as a standard action, the leaf bunny pulls a carrot out and chews on it healing herself for 1d4+1 point of damage. Familar The master of a leaf bunny familiar gains a +3 bonus on Acrobatics checks."
      ]
